    "updated_at": "2023-04-06T12:26:58Z",
    "body": "I do not think so, as it still happened even with all non-ascii characters deleted from the config file:\r\nBelow you can see how the additional space in the `cmd_duration` module makes the difference.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69082876/230378394-47cbb949-54e4-48f2-a802-60e905b85467.png)\r\n\r\nthe config:\r\n```\r\nadd_newline = false\r\nformat = \"\"\"\r\n$username$hostname[](black)[─](bold black)$directory$git_branch$git_status\\\r\n[$fill](bold black)\\\r\n$cmd_duration\\\r\n[$fill](bold black)\\\r\n$time\r\n$character\"\"\"\r\n\r\n[fill]\r\nsymbol = '-'\r\nstyle = '$style'\r\n\r\n[hostname]\r\nformat = '[@$hostname](bold yellow bg:black)'\r\nssh_symbol = \"\"\r\n\r\n[username]\r\nformat = '[$user](bold blue bg:black)'\r\nshow_always = true\r\n\r\n[cmd_duration]\r\nmin_time = 500\r\nformat = \"\"\"[[](black) \\\r\n[$duration](bold yellow bg:black)  \\\r\n[](black)](bg:black)\"\"\"\r\n\r\n[directory]\r\ntruncation_length = 3\r\nhome_symbol = \"\"\r\nformat = \"\"\"[](black)\\\r\n[$path](yellow bg:black)[$read_only]($read_only_style)\\\r\n[](black)\"\"\"\r\n\r\n[directory.substitutions]\r\n\"Documents\" = \"\"\r\n\"Downloads\" = \"\"\r\n\"Music\" = \"\"\r\n\"Pictures\" = \"\"\r\n\r\n[git_branch]\r\nsymbol = \"\"\r\nformat = '[[[─](black) $symbol $branch](bold green bg:black)]($style)'\r\n\r\n[git_status]\r\nformat = '[[[ ](bg:black)($all_status$ahead_behind) ](green bg:black)[](black)]($style)'\r\n\r\n[time]\r\ndisabled = false\r\ntime_format = \"%R\"                                      # Hour:Minute Format\r\nstyle = \"bg:#1d2230\"\r\nformat = '[[](black)[ $time ](blue bg:black)]($style)'\r\n\r\n[character]\r\nsuccess_symbol = '[y](bold green) '\r\nerror_symbol = '[n](bold red) '\r\n1\r\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
