    "updated_at": "2025-02-10T16:50:28Z",
    "body": "Just want to add an example where we want to use fill module:\n\nI'm using starship with [xonsh shell](https://xon.sh/) via [xontrib-prompt-bar](https://github.com/anki-code/xontrib-prompt-bar) and it will be cool to have a pure starship appearance as an alternative e.g.\n\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bab19b17-90ee-46af-9077-a2cf38a9d4d4)\n\nOr [this](https://github.com/anki-code/bar-theme):\n\n<img width=\"900\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7f4f9bb2-e1cf-414c-b485-c831b24c89d4\" />\n\nAlso the [discussion](https://github.com/starship/starship/discussions/6515#discussioncomment-12121999).",
