    "updated_at": "2025-04-10T12:05:19Z",
    "body": "How to force background color for `$all` elements?\n\nMy best try:\n\n<img width=\"925\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f7120359-9014-4bcb-8d17-c237775779ab\" />\n\n<details>\n\n```ini\n# ~/.config/starship.toml\n\nformat = \"\"\"[$all](bg:#222222)$fill$time$line_break$character\"\"\"\n\n[fill]\nsymbol = ' '\nstyle = 'bg:#222222'\n\n[character]\nsuccess_symbol = \"[@](bold green)\"\nerror_symbol = \"[@](bold red)\"\n\n[time]\ndisabled = false\ntime_format = \"%H:%M:%S\"\nstyle = \"bg:#222222\"\nformat = '[$time]($style)'\n```\n\n</details>",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "pin": null,
